t we tooth because they look everything over . it be a very nice transport , young woman , professional young woman .", "you know , they be different . and they be shoot they on a hill there . they make they undress , and they be beat . some of they who do not want to , they would machine-gun everyone . and sometimes they make they dig they own ditch .", "there be not mass killing , except when they bring in people from the outside , yes . we do not see they be -- but we know because they take so many young people to dig up ditch , you know . and they would bring truckload of people daily , shoot -- make they undress . they would beat they to undress and shoot they and bury they -- and then have to bury they . I have one friend who survive .", "we do not see they be -- but we know because they take so many young people to dig up ditch , you know . and they would bring truckload of people daily , shoot -- make they undress . they would beat they to undress and shoot they and bury they -- and then have to bury they . I have one friend who survive . he be Jew , he be shoot in he arm .", "he take they all three out , and he beat they severely , you know , with some kind of whip . he make he walk to a point , you know , only maybe 100 , 200 foot . make they undress , he be beat they . it be a -- he get they help , they rip they clothes and he shoot they . just like that .", "I must have , yes . because when we come to Mauthausen , we come there at night . they undress we completely , we have to undress . nude . not only that , we have to go on a chair or table and they look all over you body and in you rectum .", "well , by then I be 17 , so I go into the camp and all the rest of the people -- I mean , the older people , and the people -- the child go to the gas chamber . but we do not know that . so when we get to the camp , we be first -- they undress we . we be send to the sauna , and in the sauna -- they cut we hair before that . they cut we hair , and then we be tattoo .", "unfortunately what he would say have be true . from there I go , I be transfer to Gestapo headquarters , Gestapo mean secret state police . and that be quite a terror , because I be beat , kick and I have to clean my own blood and my own vomit and then I be call before a man , I be ask to undress , and one look at my penis , and he look at the other and say , he be jewish . I should explain that there be man who be bear almost circumcise and I be one of they . matter of fact when I be oh , I guess 11 , I begin to masturbate and that cause a little problem , it cause pain and like in most case , like circumcision of the Jews , they just stretch the foreskin and then cut it , so it kind of roll back and the whole head of the penis be expose .", "and they take they and they shoot they there . they bring we information , for example , that one of my cousin , get out from the grave and he say , if you want , I will give you the hair off my head , but shoot we right . because about , they be all , they make they undress and they be shoot they and they be fall into the grave . but some be not shoot . they cover they when they be still alive .", "none of they could speak Polish . they need a translator for I . and I be strip of citizenship , of my belongings . whatever be mine be no longer mine and get six year hard labor , whatever . then I be put in the infamous rakayetska -lrb- ph -rrb- prison in Warsaw .", "on one of those broadcast from London , they be talk about civilian laborer who go to work in Germany from Belgium and from other country and the german use they until they be completely use up , totally wear out from the hard work and they tell they that they be go to send they to a place for recreation and they take they to a place which be , look like a shower and once they be in the shower , they drop the gas bomb in and they kill they all and then they burn they . so , in other word , I hear this from London , but the scenario be different , the place be different and as I find out , as we know , London be lie on many occasion and they be try to discourage hungarian christian from go to work as volunteer in Germany , for labor . and so , once somebody mention gas chamber , I know the whole story , I mean I know where , what it be about and then we be stand in this courtyard and just stand there naked and standing and standing and wait and then come in two prisoner with number tattoo on they forearm . Q : some prisoner come in ? a : mm-hm .", "by the way , it do not matter to anybody if there be 88 of we in that boxcar when we arrive and I just could not understand they because it be so important that 88 people should be in it , that nobody should escape and here it do not matter any more , no not at all . it be just one absurd thing after another , it be like a world completely topsy-turvy , it be just . and when we be stand there naked , wait to be process or whatever , the woman run by naked , scream . the same , we woman who get separate from we and who do not have child and who be select for labor , but my mother tell I many a year later , she say , I see you , but I be naked and you be naked so I would not say anything , ? _ or anything .", "it be just one absurd thing after another , it be like a world completely topsy-turvy , it be just . and when we be stand there naked , wait to be process or whatever , the woman run by naked , scream . the same , we woman who get separate from we and who do not have child and who be select for labor , but my mother tell I many a year later , she say , I see you , but I be naked and you be naked so I would not say anything , ? _ or anything . and then eventually a ss who be process they and who be chase they to the shower , he pull down the curtain for they so they would not have to be there , expose , naked .", "the same , we woman who get separate from we and who do not have child and who be select for labor , but my mother tell I many a year later , she say , I see you