ay naked at the top of the corpse . and drive , they drive to the big ditch and bury the people . and I know that the truck be go back and forth , and back and forth , with all the dead people .", "a : allow I to take off my jacket . Q : good for you ! a : I will not strip , do not worry ! Q : would it be okay if I sit in between the two of you ? a : I do not mind .", "Q : but that be what I mean . a : that be what I just say . that everybody who have something could bring it in because nobody , they do not have to undress , like when they go to the camp in Auschwitz , they have to completely strip and everything be take away from they . so , naturally , people come into the ghetto with whatever valuable they have . but they do not hide .", "and they take we to that Monowitz , Auschwitz III , middle of the night and then as I disembark from the , unload from the truck , they take we to the , to the shower room , some kind of a shower room and so forth and there I receive my first , my first knock from a ss because I be talk and he be behind and he give I a punch in the face and , I never have one like that before . so we enter , there be a guy there , a prisoner , speak french and translate , well , tell we what to do . undress , everybody undress , so forth . once we be naked , there be a intimidation beating of a prisoner . a ss be there and the two , two Poles come and they take somebody in the group and they , they beat he , you know __________ , to show what it be , what we have to expect if we ... and I do not know if they kill he but the guy be on the floor and we be already , the message pass through .", "so we enter , there be a guy there , a prisoner , speak french and translate , well , tell we what to do . undress , everybody undress , so forth . once we be naked , there be a intimidation beating of a prisoner . a ss be there and the two , two Poles come and they take somebody in the group and they , they beat he , you know __________ , to show what it b