member , but I think once a week or once every ten day . when we arrive there , we undress , they take we clothes , they put it through the same function , like they give we - okay , what they have to do to put this stuff to disinfect all the dress . so , they give we - they take another bunch that they already disinfect from another group , and they give it to we , and we have a new dress , but each time it be a new old dress . each time , I have to fight to get the longest , but I be very lucky .", "he put everybody out because we have like a long , they call a barrack , a long , like , a factory make from brick which the people what they come before we they build themselves -- they make the people build this barracks and there be very primitive -- there be no quarter , nothing . just be , just like to shelter from the rain . so he take everybody out from the barracks with very big reflector , very big light , naked , completely naked and you have to hold you hand up . that mean , you could not have nothing hide , and with very big lamp , look over you and he have a left side and a right side and we never know , which be the good side -- the left side or the right side . they say , people say , between they that when the selection some people what they take it out , they go to go to the crematorium .", "she have gallbladder operation in the ghetto , and she have a open wound . the scar be not completely heal . well , when she be naked , I be afraid they would see this , they would send she to the gas chamber . so , I do not know what to do with myself . put she in front of I , then she would be send to the gas chamber .", "I say , `` thank God , everything would end . '' and I look on the shower that the gas should come out and I see water be come out . we be naked . all the dress be out . how can you believe it ?", "Winter , 40 degree , wet , everybody grab a dress and when it come to I , I do not have a dress . everything be take . there be ten girl leave naked . they probably grab two dress . no , they say grab -- some people want to survive .", "they probably grab two dress . no , they say grab -- some people want to survive . I be leave naked with ten other girl . then they start to whip we . we have to run to the barrack naked .", "I be leave naked with ten other girl . then they start to whip we . we have to run to the barrack naked . when I come to my barrack naked , we be stand and shiver -- no clothes . O.K. .", "then they start to whip we . we have to run to the barrack naked . when I come to my barrack naked , we be stand and shiver -- no clothes . O.K. . then the stubabba -lsb- ? -rsb-", "so she come over and she bring all ten of we a quilt to cover . so we do not know what to do . should we lay down on the mud or cover ourselves , or should we put it on the mud , the blanket , and lay naked ? they always use to take I in the middle , because I do not know why . I must have look terrible , I must be very thin or something because they always say you go to freeze to death .", "we put the quilt on the mud . I , we be stay five day like this . naked completely . jf : all ten of you be like this ? SA : all ten of we , yes .", "SA : No resistance whatsoever . I be tell that there be a few people that they bring they there . there be one girl , she be in the show business from french , and they tell she to take off the clothes , naked . so she take the gun from the german soldier and she kill he . but she be bright , fresh .", "these photo be never recover . after I be tear from my family , S.S. soldier with full equipment and police dog escort we to the bath house . we be take into a large hall and be order to undress completely naked . we be to leave we clothes on the floor . after be undressed , we be take individually to another room , where we be examine and search again .", "we learn to live with these unbelievable atrocity . after the six week of quarantine , instead of the normal head count , we be make to line up for another selection of those who would be pick out to die . we be order to parade naked in front of two row of nazi officer . we find out later that the head of the nazi officer be the infamous Dr. Mengele . he wear white glove , and with the movement of he wrist he hand motion either to the right or to the left .", "and there be like jewish policeman , a sanitary committee it be call , and they be also there . so I say to they , `` go to the family . let they give I a shirt or a coat ; you can not take out naked people . '' Q : this be everyone in the hospital they want to take out ? a : right .", "I be alone . my sister , my brother-in-law , and my niece go to Auschwitz a day before I go , and then after the selection , we be take to out bath . we be undress on this side , take a bath , and go out the other side . on the other side there stand a table with some dress , and a dress be throw to you . I have a black dress , a long black dress .", "so , whatever we be wear , pants -- tear , not tear -- shorts , long sleeve shirt , a belt and of course the wooden clog -- which the girl wear it now and enjoy it so much . we never take it in to sell because every time I look at it I think , `` my God , my God . '' so we have to take it and tie it together ; we be completely naked . that be the end of 1944 , in December , and the snow be three or four or five foot high . they close the barracks and explode bomb in the barracks .", "Q : cauldron . a : yes , and we throw we clothing in there . then when it boil -- meanwhile , we stand naked for a whole night and a whole day -- then they take it out from the water and they throw it on the roof so it freeze . then they pull it down from the roof , and we have the number , besides on we , on we jacket ; in other word , you be a number , you have no name , you be call a number . then you take the frozen clothes and you take they apart , and it break , it tear ; you put it on because it be yours , it have you number and everything , and we be leave with one leg and one without ; you have half a shirt or you have no shirt at all , it fall apart completely .", "if not enough die in a specific time or not enough be shoot in a specific time and it be get overcrowded they just bring a truck , pile they up on the truck , and take they to the crematorium . this be a daily routine and you get so use to it . it be like a doctor perform a operation , it be nothing ; you sleep with the dead and you eat with the dead , and you lay near they , and you be like a animal , strip of everything . you only object be for food and for survival , and after the war that be the thing that most of we think . I must do it , I must survive and tell the story .", "the forest have Germany and Poland on both side , full of they . and in the forest when it get dark we see a lot of Germans , officer come in and take off they uniform and change into civilian clothing . now a lot of boy -- and this my husband tell I many time -- get shot because they have take the german uniform because they be naked and they want to warm themselves , so they put on the german uniform and the Allies mistake they for Ger -- man by the end of the war and they shoot they . I be liberate May 8th . now at that time there be already some camp that be liberate .", "in order to save my skin , not to lose my leg , they have take a knife , and cut the shoe off with my skin , together . they have no bandage . she take a old sheet , rip it in strip ; she put on some salve . she say to this young man , `` do not worry , you can leave , and I will put she on a sled and take she back , '' because she think it would be too traumatic for I to ride a horse 35 mile . `` I will put she on a sled , and I will take she back where she belong . ''", "the only thing what we know , when the people come in from different city where it be more dangerous than by we , so they come in , so they tell , `` the Germans be do this , the Germans be do that . '' one te