at we have ? we be so nebbesh -lsb- helpless -rsb- for the other , but we feel good ... ashamed to tell you , but it be like this . we could cool we body on the wet window , the window be wet from the heat , and the wetness feel good on we naked chest . and we have to sew on those Mogen Dovids on the prisoner ' clothing and the number . everybody on the floor , one after the other , have to sit up , have to take off the jacket , have to give it to we .", "180 Jews angetreten zum -lsb- fall in -rsb- to Appell . ten death lay next to we ... ten dead . naked . I do not tell you everything , do not think , if I can tell you everything , we stay here until tomorrow . I can not tell you everything .", "in this little bit water , would not let they get out , hit they on the head with the iron part of the shovel . Q : when you be work in these field , be you still in those german uniform that you have be give in Sachsenhausen ? a : no , in Dachau we become -lsb- get -rsb- strip uniform . Blue and white striped uniform . pants the same .", "Q : how long have this be since you arrive at Dachau ? a : maybe a couple of month later ... maybe May , or April of 1941 . suddenly we see far away naked woman run ... it be far away , but I could see it be woman , naked . run for the S.S. ... the S.S. be stand and they be run ... be a selection of woman ... far away , of the same place , but far away . I do not know what happen to they .", "run for the S.S. ... the S.S. be stand and they be run ... be a selection of woman ... far away , of the same place , but far away . I do not know what happen to they . but we could see the naked woman , and we be stand naked , for hour , and then the sun go away , and ... it get cloudy , you know . the sun hide under the cloud . under the cloud we start to freezing , you know .", "to heal we , or what , we body . they put we on those straw , burlap bag with straw and we have to lay there a whole day , do nothing . only like naked . they give one to another shirt , I do not know what it be . every two or three day they come in , with some salve and we have to , a black salve , and put this on we body .", "so my sister say to I , `` please , quick , take off my earring because otherwise they be rip through the ear hole , '' and we have to give they away everything that we have , the rest of we little few belongings . a few picture we have we have to turn in . we have everything we have to leave in one room and then all naked we go out into another room , and then they give we the striped uniform with a wooden shoe , to go to work . NL : you sister work in the same place ? mp : we work in the same place .", "when we come there to the kitchen the guard search I and another two girl , and he find the two potato . so I be punish by give I 25 with a rubber whip on my body ; 25 time he hit I with a rubber on my body , and then I have some hair grow back . so for punishment and to dehumanize I , he make I here like a strip , to cut like a strip , so one side be a little bit of hair and the other side a little bit of hair . NL : this be a german ? mp : this be the Germans , the guard , the Germans .", "on this ship be people from the Kitchener Camp , which have be empty , and all these people be intern . the Kitchener Camp be the refugee camp establish in England to receive those who have come from Buchenwald and Sachsenhausen and other concentration camp , on they way to America , as a transfer station . however , not only be we treat very badly on this ship , people have they life 's belongings with they , document of book they have write , jewelry , anything of value be strip from they . the luggage that they have be open up , and partially throw into the sea , partially the soldier take it for themselves . those who protest be roughly handle , and we finally get on we way .", "we be examine by a doctor . I be 13 and some . I be menstruate the second time in my life , and I have to walk naked in front of this doctor 