courtyard , in the major courtyard , consist of roughly six thousand human . as we travel around the camp , additional smaller pile of body be present .", "it be just like Dante 's Inferno . that it look like . and they be unload the people so they , and they have to undress right there , and they be shoot . so they hide . they be smart two kid .", "you know , so you do not have to worry about it . '' so we go into this barrack . we have to undress , completely naked , and there be barber there . and then it be thousand of people there , light , you know , and table . and the S.S. be there .", "NL : seldom . hf : yeah . most of the time we undress on the outside , go in the shower . even in the middle of winter no matter how cold it be we always undress on the outside , leave we clothes on the outside , go inside , shower , come out again , put on we clothes again . NL : yeah .", "hf : yeah . most of the time we undress on the outside , go in the shower . even in the middle of winter no matter how cold it be we always undress on the outside , leave we clothes on the outside , go inside , shower , come out again , put on we clothes again . NL : yeah . but now at Auschwitz you get it , be it hot water ?", "anything at all ? any remnant of they former life ? kf : no , because they have be strip . when they be put in concentration camp , they be just strip of the gold in they tooth . they be strip of all , any jewelry .", "any remnant of they former life ? kf : no , because they have be strip . when they be put in concentration camp , they be just strip of the gold in they tooth . they be strip of all , any jewelry . they be strip of any clothing they have .", "kf : no , because they have be strip . when they be put in concentration camp , they be just strip of the gold in they tooth . they be strip of all , any jewelry . they be strip of any clothing they have . as you will see in one of these picture ... pile of body of clothing that be just put off for trash .", "whe